commitResults.messageBody: Update DeveloperGuide.md to the details of this current iteration
View Command is currently does not close automatically, let's update it such that windows are automatically closed at the moment when users open a new one.

This current commit will bring the UI up to date with previous discussions, and implement the Single Page View with Close command.

Tests have also been implemented.
This commit will add new user stories and use cases.

This commit will fix the following functionality issues:
- View Window closes when "exit" is called
- View Window now updates when the address book is edited.
